# Do Not Edit Translation Files

Never modify files under `server-core/src/main/java/io/onedev/server/web/translation/`,
including `Translation_*.java` (e.g. `Translation_de.java`, `Translation_fr.java`).

When adding or changing user-visible text:

If a task would require translation file updates, stop after the source-code
change and tell the user that translations need to be updated outside this
workflow.
